ARM: exynos_defconfig: Enable LEDS for Odroid-XU3/XU4

Odroid XU3 family boards come with RGB LEDs. Enabling LEDS_GPIO and
LEDS_PWM allows monitoring the board alive state (heartbeat) and
MMC/SDcard IO usage.

